latestIgtvVideos.caption:
homemade kalonji hair oil for fast, long & thick hair growth  कलौंजी+मेथी का तेल  Pratibha Salian

Also subscribe to my youtube channel for more such diys and makeup tutorials. 

Please comment down below if you find this video useful

Ingredients 

Kalonji *(Nigella seeds)

Methi seeds

Onion

Curry leaves

Coconut oil

Mustard oil

Make a powder of kalonji, methi, onion & curry leaves in a blender directly

Then take 1/2 cup coconut oil and take 1/2 cup mustard oil boil it together on low flame for 20 minutes and then pour it in a glass bottle.

Then keep the bottle in sunlight for 7 days and then start using the oil. See the magic happening :)

You can store the oil for 2-3 weeks.

Apply it on scalp keep for 1 hour and then give hot towel steam for 5 minutes and then wash it off with herbal shampoo
